	<LINE>(4.) Abuse of the Book Post.</LINE>
	<LINE>It wiU be seen from the foregoing rules, that</LINE>
	<LINE>there is no legal way of sending a letter, other</LINE>
	<LINE>than a circular letter, through the post for a postage</LINE>
	<LINE>of a halfpenny, except by means of a post card.</LINE>
